	<t3>
		<base>base-bs3</base>
	</t3>
	<description>
		<![CDATA[
		<div align="center">
			<div class="alert alert-success" style="background-color:#DFF0D8;border-color:#D6E9C6;color: #468847;padding: 1px 0;">
				
				<h3><a href="//www.joomlart.com/joomla/templates/ja-playschool">Creative and colorful Joomla template - JA PlaySchool</a></h3>
				
				<h4><a href="//www.joomlart.com/joomla/templates/ja-playschool" title="">Home</a> | <a href="//joomlart.com/demo/#ja_playschool" title="">Demo</a> | <a href="http://www.joomlart.com/documentation/joomla-templates/ja-playschool" title="">Document</a> | <a href="//pm.joomlart.com/browse/JATCPLAYSC" title="">Changelog</a></h4>

				<p>JA Playschool is dedicated Joomla template for Playschool and Kindergarten website with creative, colorful design style. JA Playschool comes with flexible layout system and number of pre-made pages with beautiful typo: Programmes, Career, Gallery and social page built with JomSocial. The template also supports all Joomla default pages.</p>

				<span style="color:#FF0000">Note: T3 blank requires T3 plugin to be installed and enabled.</span><p></p>
				<p>Copyright 2004 - 2018 <a href='http://www.joomlart.com/' title='Visit Joomlart.com!'>JoomlArt.com</a>.</p>
			</div>
			<style>table.adminform{width: 100%;}</style>
		</div>
		]]>
	</description>
